From 372407d326de01e1c0b66bc30bc3334a555b0366 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.com>
Date: Wed, 29 Apr 2026 14:46:06 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] media: imx355: Remove link_freq_index from each mode as
 ununsed

The link_freq_index value in imx355_mode is unused, so remove it.

Reviewed-by: Jacopo Mondi <jacopo.mondi@ideasonboard.com>
Signed-off-by: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.com>
